        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 text-sm max-w-md">
          A modern CSS component library built with simplicity and performance in mind. Create beautiful interfaces with minimal effort.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-4">
          <a
